<item>
            <title>[SOLR-684] Hudson builds do not have the SVN revision because svnversion is not available</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-684</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The build file tries to run svnversion when generating the jar manifest to include the revision number. This fails in Hudson however as the svnversion executable is not available.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This could be addressed by installing svnversion on the build machine or using alternative means of determining the revision number.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12401958">SOLR-684</key>
